OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779552673
OL,3,CHuge delays and tailbacks as emergency
OL,4,Crepairs are carried out on major bridge
OL,6,FDrivers have been facing huge traffic
OL,7,Fcongestion after the northbound
OL,8,FSheppey Crossing was closed.
OL,10,FThe A249 has been shut between the
OL,11,FB2005 (Iwade) and the A2500 (Minster
OL,12,Fon Sea, Sheppey) to allow for
OL,13,Femergency bridge joint repairs to take
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,FNational Highways contractors are on
OL,17,Fscene carrying out the works.
OL,19,FDue to the nature of the repairs, the
OL,20,Fclosure of the bridge is likely to be
OL,21,Fprotracted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
