OL,3,CHuge delays and tailbacks as emergency
OL,4,Crepairs are carried out on major bridge
OL,6,FThere is currently no estimated time
OL,7,Fof when the bridge will re-open.
OL,9,FRoad users heading north are advised
OL,10,Fto follow the Hollow Diamond diversion
OL,11,Fsymbol on road signs:
OL,13,FNational Highways said: "If this
OL,14,Fclosure impacts on your planned route,
OL,15,Fplease allow extra journey time.
OL,17,F"Plan ahead, you may wish to re-route
OL,18,For even delay your journey.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
