OL,6,F"Further information is available from
OL,7,FNational Highways by visiting our
OL,8,Fwww.trafficengland.com website and
OL,9,Ftravel apps, or via our regional X
OL,10,Ffeed.
OL,12,F" Our 24/7 contact centre team is also
OL,13,Favailable to provide up to the minute
OL,14,Finformation on 0300 123 5000."
